  <slide>
    <title>Purpose of SkipTo</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Support WCAG SC 2.4.1 Bypass Blocks requirement.</li>
        <li>Raise awareness of the functional use of landmark regions and headers.</li>
        <li>Improve navigation to document content for everyone.</li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
  </slide>

  <slide>
    <title>Major Changes in SkipTo Version 5.x</title>
    <contents>
      <ul>
        <li>Use scripted shortcut key to improve consistency between browsers:
          <ul>
            <li>Alt-0 (Windows/Linux)</li>
            <li>Option-0 (macOS)</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Support custom web components.</li>
        <li>Button switches to SkipTo icon on small screens.</li>
        <li>Simplify operation and configuration options.</li>
        <li>Color theme includes a new way to automatically apply a theme using:
          <ul>
            <li>hostname selector</li>
            <li>path selector</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Automatic color theme detection defined for the following host names: 
          <ul>
            <li>illinois.edu</li>
            <li>uic.ede</li>
            <li>uis.edu</li>
            <li>uillinois.edu</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </contents>
  </slide>

